title: Massive One Bedroom, SUPER Close to Downtown!
posting_body: ['Property Listing # 1913', 'Welcome home to this new, 2015 built luxury apartment community in gorgeous Austin, TX!', 'Here you can enjoy living just minutes away from downtown Austin, yet being tucked away amidst a tranquil Hill Country setting.', 'These apartments are located within Barton Creek and offers both Hill Country and downtown Austin views!', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', '10 Minutes to Hill Country Galleria', '15 Minutes from Downtown Austin', 'Bark Park', 'Beautiful Landscaping', 'Bicycle Racks Throughout The Community', 'Dog Wash Station', 'Gated Access', 'Guest Parking', 'LEED Certified', 'On-Call Maintenance', 'On-Site Maintenance', 'Poolside Cabanas With Charging Stations', 'Resident Poolside Lounge', 'Resort Style Swimming Pool With Lap Lanes', 'State-of-the-Art Athletic Center', 'Surrounded by the Barton Creek Habitat Preserve', 'Up and Coming Retail Nearby', 'Wi-fi Access in Common Areas', 'APARTMENT FEATURES:', '17 Ft Vaulted Ceilings *', 'Hickory Hardwood Floors', 'Balcony/Patio/Fenced Yards', 'Carpeted Floors from Recycled Fibers', 'Central Air/Heating', 'Downtown/Hill Country Views', 'Enhanced Sound Insulation Features', 'Fenced Yards', 'Full-size Washer/Dryer', 'LED Lighting', 'Nest Thermostats', 'Oversized Tub and Walk-in Shower *', 'Polished Concrete Flooring *', 'Quartz Countertops Throughout', 'Solar Shades', 'Stainless Steel Energy Star Appliances', 'Vaulted Ceilings', 'Views Available *', 'Walk-In Closets', 'White Cabinetry Throughout', 'Matt Davidson', 'Dash Realty', 'Apartment locator', 'Property Listing # 1913']
